\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Capacity threshold for GRPO on GSM8K (training-set reward, LoRA rank 32). (a)~Mean reward per step: Qwen3.5-4B saturates near 85\% by step 10; Qwen3-8B fluctuates (peak 87.5\%, last-10 30.5\%); Llama-3.2-3B stays below 3\%. (b)~Zero-loss decomposition: 3B zero-loss originates from all-incorrect groups (no reward signal); 4B zero-loss from all-correct groups (productive saturation). Dashed line marks 50\% reward.}}{7}{figure.caption.11}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:capacity}{{1}{7}{Capacity threshold for GRPO on GSM8K (training-set reward, LoRA rank 32). (a)~Mean reward per step: Qwen3.5-4B saturates near 85\% by step 10; Qwen3-8B fluctuates (peak 87.5\%, last-10 30.5\%); Llama-3.2-3B stays below 3\%. (b)~Zero-loss decomposition: 3B zero-loss originates from all-incorrect groups (no reward signal); 4B zero-loss from all-correct groups (productive saturation). Dashed line marks 50\% reward}{figure.caption.11}{}}
