\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces GRPO training diagnostics on arithmetic (Qwen3-8B, $G{=}4$, 25 steps). Left: policy entropy collapses from 0.773 to 0.0002 ($>$3 orders of magnitude). Center: fraction of mixed-reward groups drops from 81\% to $<$4\% by step 4. Right: mean reward saturates near 1.0 by step 5. These metrics were logged only for the arithmetic task; comparable telemetry is unavailable for GSM8K runs.}}{8}{figure.caption.12}\protected@file@percent }
