\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Tool-calling reward over training steps for synthetic vs.\ real schemas (Qwen3-8B, $G{=}8$, LoRA rank 32). Synthetic 5-tool tasks (upper curve) saturate above 0.8 reward within 5 steps. Real-world xlam-60k schemas (lower curve) plateau at 0.06--0.36 after 100 steps, a 3--8$\times $ difficulty gap. $y$-axis: mean binary reward; $x$-axis: GRPO training steps.}}{9}{figure.caption.13}\protected@file@percent }
